WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.629
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.639 --> 00:00:03.990
Well, we're going to take communion

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.150
today. I have some stuff

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:07.850
on my heart to talk to you all about. He

00:00:07.860 --> 00:00:10.629
said to me, 'During this great

00:00:10.639 --> 00:00:13.990
revival that's about to take place,

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:15.749
you are about to see something that

00:00:15.759 --> 00:00:18.390
you've never seen before.'When I was

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:22.470
praying into the harvest,

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:25.590
he showed me the glory cloud again. And

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:28.150
he said, 'Brandon, you will see the

00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:31.189
glory cloud, but it won't happen very

00:00:31.199 --> 00:00:32.950
often.'He

00:00:32.960 --> 00:00:34.310
said, 'That's something that I did in

00:00:34.310 --> 00:00:34.320
the past.'But

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:37.510
he said, 'Behold,

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:40.950
I'm going to do all things new.

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:44.069
I am going to bring forth new rivers,

00:00:44.079 --> 00:00:47.510
new oases in the desert.'He said,

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:50.950
'There will be in the days

00:00:50.950 --> 00:00:50.960
ahead.'Listen

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:53.670
to me. This will bless you.

00:00:53.680 --> 00:00:58.069
In the days ahead, a great refreshing

00:00:58.079 --> 00:01:02.790
is coming to the ones that are dry.

00:01:02.800 --> 00:01:06.870
A great river is coming.

00:01:06.870 --> 00:01:06.880
And

00:01:06.880 --> 00:01:09.109
he showed me, he said, 'Brandon,

00:01:09.119 --> 00:01:10.950
whenever the healing

00:01:10.960 --> 00:01:13.350
revival and the tent revival

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:17.429
started with Jack Coe

00:01:17.429 --> 00:01:17.439
and Oral

00:01:17.439 --> 00:01:19.830
Roberts and William Brandon and

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:22.469
all them, they would pray for people—and

00:01:22.469 --> 00:01:22.479
A.A.

00:01:22.479 --> 00:01:25.429
Allen, they would pray for

00:01:25.429 --> 00:01:25.439
people—and

00:01:25.439 --> 00:01:27.030
you didn't see anybody

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:28.789
falling out like they do now with the

00:01:28.799 --> 00:01:30.310
courtesy falls. A lot of people

00:01:30.320 --> 00:01:33.270
fall out.

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:35.190
You see a lot of that stuff and you

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:37.910
wonder, 'Is this performance or is it

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:39.749
authentic?'I

00:01:39.759 --> 00:01:42.710
have experienced the authentic.

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:45.990
But whenever we first saw the

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:49.590
healing movement of the tent

00:01:49.600 --> 00:01:50.950
revival, you didn't see anybody falling

00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:52.710
in those tents. I didn't, at least. And

00:01:52.720 --> 00:01:54.710
when I watch the old revival, I go

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:57.109
through and watch the old videos on

00:01:57.119 --> 00:01:59.429
YouTube that started with Kathryn

00:01:59.429 --> 00:01:59.439
Kuhlman.

00:01:59.439 --> 00:02:01.270
It looked like—from what I

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:02.709
understand, from what I'm trying to

00:02:02.709 --> 00:02:02.719
pinpoint—and

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:04.709
correct me if I'm

00:02:04.719 --> 00:02:07.350
wrong, any of you elders, if you saw

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:09.350
people fall out in tent revivals,

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:12.710
then I'm wrong. But the Lord showed me

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:16.309
that that really started to take off

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:19.830
during Kathryn Kuhlman and Benny Hinn

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:21.830
and some of the others. And

00:02:21.840 --> 00:02:23.750
now it happens all the time;

00:02:23.760 --> 00:02:25.430
you see them pray for people, people fall

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:27.350
out.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:29.030
And it was a wave, and then it was the

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:31.030
holy laughter and the shaking, and all

00:02:31.040 --> 00:02:33.509
that happened with Rodney Howard-Browne, and

00:02:33.519 --> 00:02:36.070
that happened a lot in the '90s. Then it

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:39.190
went into the early 2000s and so on,

00:02:39.200 --> 00:02:42.869
right? So the Lord showed me, he said,

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:46.790
'Behold, I'm going to do something

00:02:46.790 --> 00:02:46.800
new.'And

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:49.350
I had an open-eyed vision, and he

00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:51.830
said, 'Brandon, I saw the glory cloud

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:55.110
come in.'But he said, 'What is going to

00:02:55.120 --> 00:02:58.390
happen with this last outpouring, this

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:00.949
last push?'He said, 'I'm going to do

00:03:00.959 --> 00:03:03.509
something that you've never seen before.

00:03:03.519 --> 00:03:07.990
You need to start to think bigger,

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:10.710
for what has been in the past will be

00:03:10.710 --> 00:03:10.720
something—I'm

00:03:10.720 --> 00:03:12.229
going to do something

00:03:12.229 --> 00:03:12.239
new.'And

00:03:12.239 --> 00:03:16.149
I saw this

00:03:16.149 --> 00:03:16.159
blonde-headed

00:03:16.159 --> 00:03:17.670
woman. And I saw some other people come

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:21.030
down to the front of his meetings.

00:03:21.040 --> 00:03:24.790
And a tangible wind of the spirit of the

00:03:24.800 --> 00:03:29.670
Lord came in like a mighty rushing wind

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:31.910
with cloven tongues of fire like it was

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:36.149
in Acts chapter 2. And I'm

00:03:36.149 --> 00:03:36.159
talking—there's

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:38.630
no way to explain

00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:41.110
what I saw;

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:43.430
it doesn't make any sense. I

00:03:43.440 --> 00:03:46.869
saw wind blowing these women's hair like

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:49.110
a whirlwind,

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:51.830
and it was whipping their hair around

00:03:51.840 --> 00:03:54.470
and their clothes, and

00:03:54.480 --> 00:03:56.470
they actually could feel the wind of the

00:03:56.480 --> 00:03:58.949
spirit on them and they fell out that

00:03:58.959 --> 00:04:01.589
way. I saw a wind as you went. It was

00:04:01.599 --> 00:04:03.429
like the power of the Holy

00:04:03.439 --> 00:04:04.630
Spirit. It was

00:04:04.640 --> 00:04:06.550
like moving your hand,

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:10.309
and I saw the glory moving in the

00:04:10.319 --> 00:04:13.270
atmosphere, and people could feel the

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:15.429
wind of the Holy Spirit in the

00:04:15.439 --> 00:04:17.270
auditorium.

00:04:17.280 --> 00:04:19.990
And as the wind of the Holy Spirit moved

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:21.909
through the auditorium, people were

00:04:21.919 --> 00:04:23.430
getting healed and their hair was

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:26.710
actually tangibly moving.

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:28.629
And the Lord said, 'You've never seen

00:04:28.639 --> 00:04:30.230
what I'm about to do in these last

00:04:30.230 --> 00:04:30.240
days.'He

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:33.030
said that before, when

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:35.030
people would fall out, you had the people

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:38.950
in the audience saying, 'Is that real?

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:40.870
Is that real?'with the holy laughter,

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:42.790
if they're not experienced. But when

00:04:42.800 --> 00:04:47.189
you feel a tangible move of the Holy

00:04:47.199 --> 00:04:51.189
Spirit on you—like the glory cloud,

00:04:51.199 --> 00:04:54.230
everybody could sense it in Azusa

00:04:54.230 --> 00:04:54.240
Street.

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:56.070
The glory cloud—they said they played

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:58.710
with it as kids;

00:04:58.720 --> 00:05:01.830
it was a tangible,

00:05:01.840 --> 00:05:05.189
thick fog. And it even talks about it in

00:05:05.199 --> 00:05:09.270
the Bible; it filled the Holy of Holies.

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:12.390
But the Lord said to me, 'I'm going to

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:15.590
do something new and it will be a

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:17.110
refreshing,

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:20.230
for my fragrance will fill the

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:23.350
atmosphere

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:27.270
whenever people are

00:05:27.270 --> 00:05:27.280
ministering.'He

00:05:27.280 --> 00:05:29.670
said, 'You

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:34.710
will tangibly smell my fragrance, for I

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:37.110
carry a

00:05:37.110 --> 00:05:37.120
fragrance.'And

00:05:37.120 --> 00:05:40.629
it was a refreshing. When

00:05:40.639 --> 00:05:44.390
people breathe in this fragrance, the

00:05:44.400 --> 00:05:47.590
Lord said it will be like

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:49.029
something you've never smelled—like heaven

00:05:49.039 --> 00:05:52.230
on earth. Breathing in, and

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:54.870
you'll be physically healed. It will be

00:05:54.880 --> 00:05:58.870
a wind of the spirit. I saw people

00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:02.310
being touched by the Shekinah glory

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:07.029
in a different way than

00:06:07.039 --> 00:06:09.670
we've ever seen before. He's going to do

00:06:09.680 --> 00:06:12.710
something like we've never seen before.

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:15.590
And I saw the wind whipping around

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:17.670
people's hair and it was moving on them

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:20.070
and they were being refreshed.

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:23.189
And old wineskins that had turned into

00:06:23.199 --> 00:06:27.029
vinegar turned into new wine.

00:06:27.039 --> 00:06:30.230
A new fragrance, a new presence of the

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:33.430
Lord will be like an oasis in the days

00:06:33.440 --> 00:06:36.870
ahead on people in major

00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:39.430
services. And I'm telling you, they're

00:06:39.440 --> 00:06:41.909
coming from the north; I'm telling you,

00:06:41.919 --> 00:06:43.350
they're coming from the south; they're

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:44.309
coming from the east; they're coming

00:06:44.319 --> 00:06:46.469
from the west. People are

00:06:46.479 --> 00:06:49.029
hungry and they're desperate for

00:06:49.039 --> 00:06:52.390
a move of God. They're desperate for a

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:55.350
fresh touch from the Lord. And I'm

00:06:55.360 --> 00:06:57.749
telling you, he said, 'My yoke is easy

00:06:57.759 --> 00:07:00.390
and my burden is light. Come unto me all

00:07:00.400 --> 00:07:02.390
ye that are heavy laden and I will

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:04.390
give you

00:07:04.390 --> 00:07:04.400
rest.'Do

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:07.350
you understand what God is about to

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:09.990
do? We've never seen it in generations

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:12.950
past. We're going to see a fresh touch

00:07:12.960 --> 00:07:15.830
of the fire of the Holy Spirit on every

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:18.950
single person who is thirsty.

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:20.790
Those that are hungry, he said he's

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:23.430
going to give you fresh

00:07:23.430 --> 00:07:23.440
meat.

00:07:23.440 --> 00:07:27.749
Something new and tangible is coming and

00:07:27.759 --> 00:07:30.070
he's looking for an 'all hands on

00:07:30.070 --> 00:07:30.080
deck'experience

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:35.029
who will just say yes.

00:07:35.039 --> 00:07:37.029
He said he would pour out his spirit

00:07:37.039 --> 00:07:40.230
upon all flesh.

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:43.270
And I believe right now we are at that

00:07:43.280 --> 00:07:45.430
place where he said, 'Brandon, it's time

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:48.469
to become more active in fasting. It's

00:07:48.479 --> 00:07:50.950
time to become more in line with

00:07:50.960 --> 00:07:54.629
prayer and fasting. Pray

00:07:54.639 --> 00:07:57.670
and fast. Seek me daily and you will

00:07:57.680 --> 00:07:59.670
find me.'I said, 'Lord, I need a fresh touch.'Give me

00:08:07.599 --> 00:08:09.830
that living water and let

00:08:09.830 --> 00:08:09.840
it

00:08:09.840 --> 00:08:13.830
overflow. Not ministering to

00:08:13.840 --> 00:08:16.550
people out of your reserves, but

00:08:16.560 --> 00:08:18.629
ministering to my people out of the

00:08:18.639 --> 00:08:21.350
overflow of your heart. Out of the

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:25.110
overflow to the extreme,

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:28.550
to the full, until

00:08:28.550 --> 00:08:28.560
it overflows—out

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:31.909
of your belly shall flow rivers of

00:08:31.919 --> 00:08:35.110
living water. And he told me, he said,

00:08:35.120 --> 00:08:37.190
'That will come through fasting and

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:38.790
prayer,

00:08:38.800 --> 00:08:41.990
seeking me daily, and you will find

00:08:41.990 --> 00:08:42.000
me.'And

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:45.269
out of this personal, more

00:08:45.279 --> 00:08:47.990
intimate relationship with me will

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:51.110
become a greater overflow out of you for

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:53.829
the people. But you'll not get there

00:08:53.839 --> 00:08:55.990
until you have intimacy even on a

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:58.870
greater level with me.

00:08:58.880 --> 00:09:01.750
There's many of my ministers, he said,

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:03.829
that are trying to minister out of their

00:09:03.839 --> 00:09:06.630
reserves. And many of them are

00:09:06.640 --> 00:09:09.670
ministering in a dry place.

00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:12.550
But he said, 'I want you to drink from my

00:09:12.560 --> 00:09:16.550
river. Drink from the well

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:19.829
that never shall run

00:09:19.829 --> 00:09:19.839
dry.'Do

00:09:19.839 --> 00:09:25.030
you understand? 'Fill my cup, Lord.

00:09:25.040 --> 00:09:27.750
I lift it up,

00:09:27.750 --> 00:09:27.760
Lord.'That's

00:09:27.760 --> 00:09:29.590
where he's at. And

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:31.430
he told me, he said, 'He's uncapping

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:34.389
those wells of revival.'And I told you

00:09:34.399 --> 00:09:37.590
what I saw about ORU and about what he's

00:09:37.600 --> 00:09:39.430
going to do with the students there on the

00:09:39.430 --> 00:09:39.440
ORU

00:09:39.440 --> 00:09:42.070
campus. And he said, 'I'm going to

00:09:42.080 --> 00:09:45.269
bring forth a great and mighty revival

00:09:45.279 --> 00:09:47.110
with this

00:09:47.120 --> 00:09:49.269
young generation, and it will be through

00:09:49.279 --> 00:09:51.269
the Mabee Center. And I'm going to fill

00:09:51.279 --> 00:09:53.269
that Mabee Center up.'And I'm telling

00:09:53.279 --> 00:09:55.670
you, it's not going to be a convenient

00:09:55.680 --> 00:09:58.470
move with people. It's

00:09:58.480 --> 00:10:01.269
time for my bedtime.

00:10:01.279 --> 00:10:03.509
We've seen it at our church. And

00:10:03.509 --> 00:10:03.519
people—we

00:10:03.519 --> 00:10:06.310
had probably five or six families

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:08.310
that stayed, and the rest of the

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:11.190
congregation left because it got too

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:14.790
late for them. How desperate are you? How

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:19.030
hungry? How thirsty are you?

00:10:19.040 --> 00:10:22.230
How hungry? How desperate? How thirsty

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:24.310
are you?

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:26.550
Blessed are those that hunger and thirst

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:28.949
after righteousness, for they will be

00:10:28.959 --> 00:10:31.430
filled.

00:10:31.440 --> 00:10:33.269
I tell you this because it's so

00:10:33.279 --> 00:10:36.630
important that you shake off the old you

00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:38.630
and get ready for what God is about to

00:10:38.640 --> 00:10:40.150
do.

00:10:40.160 --> 00:10:43.990
When you experience the true healing

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:46.949
flow of the river of the Holy Spirit,

00:10:46.959 --> 00:10:50.470
there's no time. You can be there

00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:53.430
all night. Give me an alarm code; I'll

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:55.910
turn it on. Give me a key; I did that

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:58.069
for years. I just want

00:10:58.079 --> 00:11:03.430
to sit at the feet of Jesus.

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:07.670
Who cares about anything else?

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:10.230
There's nothing else in this earth that

00:11:10.240 --> 00:11:13.030
I want other than to be a Holy Ghost

00:11:13.040 --> 00:11:16.710
junkie, you know.

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:21.509
But I don't want to be addicted

00:11:21.519 --> 00:11:25.110
to a movement and not see

00:11:25.120 --> 00:11:27.990
people's lives changed.

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:30.790
If we get a fresh drink—if we get

00:11:30.790 --> 00:11:30.800
it—we

00:11:30.800 --> 00:11:32.710
don't want to be Holy Ghost crack

00:11:32.720 --> 00:11:35.509
addicts and not get changed, letting it

00:11:35.519 --> 00:11:36.870
change us where we're getting a Holy

00:11:36.880 --> 00:11:38.550
Ghost high every time we come in there

00:11:38.560 --> 00:11:40.310
and we're not taking it out and dumping

00:11:40.320 --> 00:11:42.949
it out on the nations.

00:11:42.959 --> 00:11:45.350
You can either let it change you, or you

00:11:45.360 --> 00:11:47.190
can be a Holy Ghost crack addict and

00:11:47.200 --> 00:11:48.949
come from one high to another high to

00:11:48.959 --> 00:11:50.790
another high and you don't do

00:11:50.800 --> 00:11:53.590
anything with it. He's not touching you

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:55.269
so you can just have your Holy Ghost

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:58.310
goosebumps, take it

00:11:58.320 --> 00:11:59.990
home and don't change, and then you come back

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:01.350
the next week and you have to be

00:12:01.360 --> 00:12:03.269
resurrected spiritually because you're

00:12:03.279 --> 00:12:05.030
spiritually dead again because you

00:12:05.040 --> 00:12:07.670
didn't take a day-to-day

00:12:07.680 --> 00:12:10.310
relationship with the Father. You only

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:12.550
got a Holy Ghost infilling on Sunday,

00:12:12.560 --> 00:12:14.470
but the rest of the week you lived like

00:12:14.480 --> 00:12:17.190
hell. The Lord wants you to come unto

00:12:17.200 --> 00:12:19.990
him and be filled and controlled by the

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:21.910
Holy Spirit every single day of your

00:12:21.920 --> 00:12:25.829
life to the overflow.

00:12:30.480 --> 00:12:32.790
He's touching

00:12:32.800 --> 00:12:35.990
you with the Holy Ghost and fire so that

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:38.389
you can take it to the generation that's

00:12:38.399 --> 00:12:41.030
dying and thirsty. They need a fresh

00:12:41.040 --> 00:12:43.350
touch from Jesus,

00:12:43.360 --> 00:12:45.430
and he wants to give it to you so you

00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:49.030
can give it to them. Let your

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:51.190
life be a light that shines unto all

00:12:51.200 --> 00:12:55.430
men, women, children, whoever. Let it

